data.description: Motivated sellers! Check out this incredible 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom house in the Klein ISD area.  Equipped with new ceiling fans in all bedrooms. With Pex piping and water softener installed, this home guarantees comfortable living for you and your loved ones. Plus, the brand new front and back doors promise optimal security and easy access to the outdoors. Bring your love and special touches.  This home is being sold "as is, where is". Conveniently located to The Vintage, 249, 99, Willowbrook Mall and Methodist Hosp. Don't let this opportunity slip away. Schedule a showing today.
